msgctxt "56_Akiyama"
msgid "(Hm?)"
msgstr "(¿Mm?)."

msgctxt "80_Woman"
msgid "No, stop it!"
msgstr "¡No! ¡Por favor, déjenme en paz!"

msgctxt "92_Cocky Punk"
msgid "What are you so worried about, honey? It's not like we're gonna take anything from you. It's all about what we're gonna <Italic>give</Italic> you, hehe!"
msgstr "Vamos, nena, no seas así. No te va a pasar nada."

msgctxt "104_Sleazy Punk"
msgid "Don't worry, we'll be sure to thank you real good once we're done. So whaddya say, baby?"
msgstr "Te vamos a compensar bien, ¿sí? Anda, no te cuesta nada."

msgctxt "116_Woman"
msgid "Someone, help!"
msgstr "¡A-alguien...! ¡Alguien, ayúdeme!"

msgctxt "128_Akiyama"
msgid "(Ugh, I don't have gas in the tank for this. But I can't just sit back and watch...)"
msgstr "(Uff... Estoy cansado, pero no puedo hacerme el loco con algo como esto)."

msgctxt "140_Akiyama"
msgid "Hey. I'd suggest leaving her alone if I were you."
msgstr "Hey, hey, chicos. Es momento de parar."

msgctxt "152_Cocky Punk"
msgid "Who's talking? We don't take advice from no-name shit off the street."
msgstr "¿Y quién mierda eres tú? ¡Ya deja de joder...!"

msgctxt "164_Akiyama"
msgid "You should start. You're never gonna get a girl if you treat them like property instead of people."
msgstr "Con esa actitud hacia las mujeres, no vas a levantar ni polvo, ¿sabías?"

msgctxt "176_Sleazy Punk"
msgid "I'll treat a broad however I want!"
msgstr "¡Cállate! ¡Nadie te pidió tu opinión!"

msgctxt "188_Cocky Punk"
msgid "Besides, who the hell do you think you are? I bet you ain't no saint yourself!"
msgstr "¿Y este tipo quién se cree que es? Se las da de buenito y todo."

msgctxt "200_Sleazy Punk"
msgid "Guess we're gonna have to educate you. And I'm not talking with a blackboard and chalk."
msgstr "Es momento de educar tu trasero, ¡ahora aprenderás a no meterte en asuntos que no te incumben, viejo!"

